OL,3,CChancellor Reeves warned of 'tough'
OL,4,Ctrade-offs ahead of spending review
OL,6,FRachel Reeves has been warned that
OL,7,F"tough trade-offs" await her at this
OL,8,Fsummer's spending review, as she has
OL,9,Fbeen urged to prioritise investment
OL,10,Fthat "boosts" public services and
OL,11,Fstandards for families.
OL,13,FA report from the Resolution
OL,14,FFoundation has suggested that the
OL,15,FGovernment should focus spending from
OL,16,Fits "limited pot" in areas such as
OL,17,Fhealth and housing if it wants to
OL,18,Fincrease living standards.
