OL,3,CChancellor Reeves warned of 'tough'
OL,4,Ctrade-offs ahead of spending review
OL,6,FThe analysis by the think tank also
OL,7,Furges ministers to examine investment
OL,8,Fat June's spending review in the
OL,9,Fprisons system and public transport,
OL,10,Fbut describes them as "secondary
OL,11,Fpriorities".
OL,13,FThe Treasury is currently undertaking
OL,14,Fthe review, which will set the budgets
OL,15,Ffor Government departments for the
OL,16,Fnext three years in terms of day-to-
OL,17,Fday spending.
