OL,3,CChancellor Reeves warned of 'tough'
OL,4,Ctrade-offs ahead of spending review
OL,6,FThe process will set the budgets for
OL,7,Fso-called unprotected departments,
OL,8,Fincluding local government, justice,
OL,9,Ftransport and culture. Protected
OL,10,Fdepartments include defence, the NHS
OL,11,Fin health, and schools as part of the
OL,12,Feducation envelope.
OL,14,F"The Chancellor must now decide how to
OL,15,Fallocate a limited pot of capital
OL,16,Fspending in a way that both addresses
OL,17,Fthe UK's legacy of frayed
OL,18,Finfrastructure and supports future
OL,19,Fambitions for growth and higher living
OL,20,Fstandards," the report stated.
OL,26,@vD@AOU|D@KO]
