OL,3,CChancellor Reeves warned of 'tough'
OL,4,Ctrade-offs ahead of spending review
OL,6,F"Focussing direct government
OL,7,Finvestment in health and housing would
OL,8,Fallow the Government to deal with the
OL,9,Flegacy they have inherited, while
OL,10,Ffurthering their missions of boosting
OL,11,Fgrowth and raising living standards."
OL,13,FCapital spending is money used to
OL,14,Fspend projects such as new hospitals
OL,15,For road schemes, rather than day-to-
OL,16,Fday running costs such as salaries.
