OL,3,CChancellor Reeves warned of 'tough'
OL,4,Ctrade-offs ahead of spending review
OL,6,FAt the budget in October 2024, Ms
OL,7,FReeves announced more money for
OL,8,Fcapital spending, but also said that
OL,9,Fthere would be "four key guardrails"
OL,10,Fintroduced to ensure good value for
OL,11,Fmoney.
OL,13,F"Ultimately, if the Government wants
OL,14,Fto avoid dramatic cuts to departmental
OL,15,Fbudgets, then it will likely have
OL,16,Faround #20-50 billion of capital
OL,17,Fspending to allocate over the next
OL,18,Ffive years," the Resolution Foundation
OL,19,Freport said.
