OL,6,FHe said that Ms Reeves "should look to
OL,7,Fprioritise investment that boosts
OL,8,Fpublic services, economic growth, and
OL,9,Ffamily living standards".
OL,11,F"Affordable housing should be targeted
OL,12,Fin major cities with acute housing
OL,13,Fneeds, where its scarcity limits
OL,14,Fliving standards and economic
OL,15,Fpotential. This investment will help
OL,16,Fcities to attract new firms and
OL,17,Fworkers ` especially if affordable
OL,18,Fhousing is complemented by better
OL,19,Fcommuter transport links," he added.
